## 8. Streamlit UI Layout Plan

To display your prototype, run three specialized apps:
1. **Simulator Terminal (Port 8501)**: Sidebar controls to adjust incident parameters, an interactive Folium click-map to place mock accidents, and resource breakdown lists.
2. **Operations Heatmap Dashboard (Port 8502)**: Shows a full Bengaluru map with coordinate density heatmaps, color-coded markers, and layer checkboxes to isolate zones.
3. **Officer Terminal & Retraining Center (Port 8503)**: A ticket closure portal for on-duty head constables to submit feedback, coupled with system drift alerts and automated model retraining graphs.

