## 11. Presentation Ideas (Pitch Structure)

1. **The Hook (1 min)**: Explain the "Gridlock Toll" of Bengaluru (e.g. average commuter loses 200 hours/year).
2. **The Innovation (2 mins)**: Emphasize the "Closed-Loop feedback" and "Self-learning" pipeline. Show how the model adapts to monsoon rain blocks without developer interventions.
3. **Live Demo (3 mins)**: Walk through the three ports: Simulator $\rightarrow$ Heatmap $\rightarrow$ Officer Feedback Form $\rightarrow$ Triggering Retraining.
4. **Impact Analysis (1 min)**: Project resource utilization savings (e.g. 22% reduction in traffic officer idle time, 18% improvement in average queue clearance rates).

